title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Add a table to the report that has a group row with a highlight rule and a map rule. 2. Preview the attached report. 3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
